timestamp.description: Time of the measurement, floored to 15 sec

xname.description: Unique identifier for the CDU of the measurement, e.g. x2007c1. The CDU xname is the xname of the neighboring cabinet

col.description: Col index of the cdu. (Note this the col of the neighboring cabinet.)

power.description: AC Input power to the CDU (unit: W, interval: 15 sec)

liquid_inlet_0_flow_primary.description: Liquid Inlet 0 Liquid Flow Primary, i.e. the facility supply flowrate (unit: gal/min, interval: 1 min)

liquid_inlet_0_temperature_primary.description: Liquid Inlet 0 Temperature Primary i.e. the facility supply temperature (unit: degC, interval: 1 min)

liquid_outlet_0_temperature_primary.description: Liquid Outlet 0 Temperature Primary i.e. the facility return temperature (unit: degC, interval: 1 min)

liquid_inlet_0_pressure_primary.description: Liquid Inlet_0 Pressure Primary i.e. the facility supply pressure (unit: lbs/in^2, interval: 1 min)

liquid_outlet_0_pressure_primary.description: Liquid Outlet 0 Pressure Primary i.e. the facility return pressure (unit: lbs/in^2, interval: 1 min)

liquid_outlet_0_flow_secondary.description: Liquid Outlet 0 Liquid Flow Secondary i.e. the rack supply flowrate (unit: gal/min, interval: 1 min)

liquid_inlet_1_temperature_secondary.description: Liquid Inlet 1 Temperature Secondary i.e. rack return temperature (unit: degC, interval: 1 min)

liquid_outlet_1_temperature_secondary.description: Liquid Outlet 1 Temperature Secondary i.e. the rack supply temperature (unit: degC, interval: 1 min)

liquid_inlet_1_pressure_secondary.description: Liquid Inlet 1 Pressure Secondary i.e. the rack return pressure (unit: lbs/in^2, interval: 1 min)

liquid_outlet_1_pressure_secondary.description: Liquid Outlet 1 Pressure Secondary i.e. the rack supply pressure (unit: lbs/in^2, interval: 1 min)

pump_1_input_pressure_secondary.description: Pump 1 Input Pressure (unit: lbs/in^2, interval: 1 min)
